{"tid":193561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 我已經痾左三十幾次…","createTime":"2017-04-09T11:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T17:49:06.000Z","uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfdd7f8677dfb16147630483b18bc75c2def33c","tid":193561,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:31:38.000Z","msg":"由琴日朝早七點開始&hellip;<br />\n到呢一刻 我已經痾左三十幾次<br />\n<br />\n我已經痾到唔知自己痾緊咩<br />\n<br />\n今日晏就去左睇醫生 但佢冇比止痾藥我<br />\n佢叫我返去食清d 痾清哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好驚我會死呀 我好辛苦呀！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21dabbbb8d2ef5e4ddfcae26cc4bc13979a8c1c5","tid":193561,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"7:00, 8:30, 9:30, 10:30, 11:15, <br />\n12:00, 1:10, 2:20, 3:05, 4:10, 5:50, <br />\n6:15, 7:10, 9:00, 10:01, 10:49, 11:45,<br />\n12:30, 1:30, 6:35, 9:20, 12:20, 1:30, <br />\n2:30, 5:30, 6:09, 6:32, 06:55, 7:15,<br />\n7:35, 8:08, 8:35, 9:05, 9:30, 9:55"},{"pid":"dbf5aecc9334becbe88a145c659ea9cd0c4f2464","tid":193561,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff616f2ccf4af9747c348691aa100a764077c8d8","tid":193561,"uid":77542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"藿香正氣水"},{"pid":"26f2b85ea2b8f277862b86991301fdcfe93aac09","tid":193561,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"花花公子成日屙屙屙 然而開不開心他都不是太清楚"},{"pid":"53a443ec662b01934f48c395fcc057ece534db38","tid":193561,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"Me too<br />\n<br />\n昨晚打完邊lo 就肚頂住頂住"},{"pid":"f4554e9409073dee85c9bcfa0e02ba7ac051bc73","tid":193561,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:39:55.000Z","msg":"打針啦"},{"pid":"d860709de40ba47eea85c89508f05dd7c5a6182c","tid":193561,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"買寶礦力，痾一次飲幾啖"},{"pid":"0289efb04e4440666958b24815ad6b1884e77964","tid":193561,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"我痾埋血色咁既野 但抹patpat冇血 我究竟係咪就死"},{"pid":"adf6c05161ad082080c4105990780bd339c73dda","tid":193561,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"絲打要唔要糖水? 我揸車順路買俾你"},{"pid":"77cc9a3cda12e92f6aa3f0a7467c145bd624ed0e","tid":193561,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"有矛事，買藥比你？"},{"pid":"8d69ec2175a66c292261fdcc509e6a01f186520c","tid":193561,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"絲打你要睇急症 <br />\n快啲打番支針先啦 <br />\n咁痾落去好大獲"},{"pid":"e9cb2d24fa793e73febd2813d189a4f3d2cb0940","tid":193561,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉 我頭先經歷左好大既恥辱<br />\n<br />\n我本身攝住個兜訓著? 個助理佢岩岩返工<br />\n之後聯同幾個助理入黎幫我推床去隔離病房<br />\n然後佢叫我自己落床 咁我同佢講我肚痾攝住左個兜<br />\n<br />\n佢把聲吊到勁高：下，點解要攝兜呀？<br />\n我：因為我頭先係廁所痛到出唔到黎&hellip; 之後姑娘就幫我攝住個兜痾<br />\n之後推左床入隔離病房之後 佢就走? 拎左我?頭個兩塊尿布走<br />\n<br />\n然後我就叫住佢：唔該，我想要返個尿布一陣自己換&hellip;<br />\n佢又係好大聲：你做咩要尿布？？<br />\n另一個行前過佢既助理回頭問做咩事<br />\n佢仍然係大聲到全房都聽到咁：佢話要尿布喎，有個兜攝住咪得囉，仲要尿布<br />\n另一個助理：咁你擺低係度啦<br />\n<br />\n我：係呀因為我想依加換，我個身好痺了<br />\n佢：咁呀，依加幫你換埋啦！點解後生細女會咁咖！<br />\n之後佢叫我拱起身比佢拎走個兜 佢見到我有m<br />\n佢又keep住咁大聲：下！你黎m呀！唔怪得知要兜又尿布啦，仲要濕哂，咁後生都落唔到床咩<br />\n我：因為我頭先真係好痛同埋係咁痾&hellip;<br />\n另一個助理對佢講：你唔好咁大聲啦，病人私隱黎<br />\n佢：咁我岩岩返工咩都唔知呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n但仿佛我已經瘀到冇頂哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b16ec33bd29daf66db3d988560661f1eea53e9f","tid":193561,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打要唔要糖水? 我揸車順路買俾你</blockquote><br />\n醫生有開電解質補充劑比我&hellip;"},{"pid":"19e352f29551d3a14c5b1dcb51af4229f33029b2","tid":193561,"uid":11296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"好似係邊到見過呢個post"},{"pid":"d70b9027134112115bdb52bf1d4047a23430f452","tid":193561,"uid":56452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:02:12.000Z","msg":"好多新會員"},{"pid":"6ca51f68c3345feb353ef29c29867d79f1958227","tid":193561,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"all in or nothing"},{"pid":"f26803dc856260641ab1effbca6ece915784af49","tid":193561,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打你要睇急症 <br />\n快啲打番支針先啦 <br />\n咁痾落去好大獲</blockquote><br />\n今日去左 吊左兩個鐘鹽水 打左枝針 六點出左院"},{"pid":"ae2a779113530eeeb9e99e4c29497da9baf28c58","tid":193561,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"我今日飲唔夠一杯水 食唔夠三份一碗粥 我好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605d6c34aa742983882ac0ca6015321bbf4001cb","tid":193561,"uid":41102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"絲打 食唔食摩打手撕雞？"},{"pid":"4eb0d2d879b3c184ed74f3bb7d7c8d7cb7efe1d9","tid":193561,"uid":54490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69593c889010a7e66385d673430eed1fc3fe09d1","tid":193561,"uid":42617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真洗唔洗幫你買？渣左車入元朗同Fd食糖水 ok ga又順路可以幫你買</blockquote><br />\n你係度講又比人話學友收兵咖？"},{"pid":"85d0b9afda741271886a2e30d420065fe77d4d30","tid":193561,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真洗唔洗幫你買？渣左車入元朗同Fd食糖水 ok